in
the
King’s
Tower.
“She
was
looking
for
you.”

“She
was
not!
Don’t
say
that!”
Sam
had
only
spoken
to
Val
twice,
when
Maester
Aemon
called
upon
her
to
make
sure
the
babes
were
healthy.
The
princess
was
so
pretty
that
he
oft
found
himself
stammering
and
