“Why
not?”
asked
Pyp.
“She
wants
to
have
your
children.
Maybe
we
should
call
you
Sam
the
Seducer.”

Sam
reddened.
King
Stannis
had
plans
for
Val,
he
knew;
she
was
the
mortar
with
which
he
meant
to
seal
the
