between
the
northmen
and
the
free
folk.
“I
don’t
have
time
for
archery
today,
I
need
to
go
see
Jon.”

“Jon?
Jon?
Do
we
know
anyone
named
Jon,
Grenn?”

“He
means
the
Lord
Commander.”

“Ohhh.
The
Great
Lord
Snow.
To
be
sure.
Why
do
you
want
to
see
him?
He
can’t
even
wiggle
his
