but
Sam
caught
her
arm,
spilling
two
books
as
he
did.
“Gilly.”

“Sam.”
Her
voice
sounded
raw.
Gilly
was
dark-haired
and
slim,
with
the
big
brown
eyes
of
a
doe.
She
was
swallowed
by
the
folds
