The
book
appeared
undamaged.
Maester
Thomax’s
Dragonkin,
Being
a
History
of
House
Targaryen
from
Exile
to
Apotheosis,
with
a
Consideration
of
the
Life
and
Death
of
Dragons
had
not
been
so
