“Yes,
but...
if
the
Lannisters
should
prevail
and
Lord
Tywin
decides
that
we
betrayed
the
king
by
aiding
Stannis,
it
could
mean
the
end
of
the
Night’s
Watch.
He
has
the
Tyrells
behind
him,
with
all
the
strength
of
Highgarden.
And
he
did
defeat
Lord
Stannis
on
