Lord
Tywin’s
eyes
are
closed
forever
now,
Cersei
thought.
It
is
my
look
they
will
flinch
from
now,
my
frown
that
they
must
fear.
I
am
a
lion
too.

It
was
gloomy
within
the
sept
with
the
sky
so
grey
outside.
If
the
rain
ever
stopped,
the
sun
would
slant
down
through
