in
the
Free
Cities.”

“Do
you
have
many
friends
across
the
water?”

“In
Myr,
many.
In
Lys
as
well,
and
Tyrosh.
Men
of
power.”

Cersei
could
well
believe
it.
The
Myrish
woman
was
too
