she’d
just
come
from
bed.
She
even
smells
of
sin,
like
some
exotic
lotus.
“Lord
Merryweather
and
I
wish
only
to
serve
Your
Grace
and
the
little
king,”
the
woman
purred,
with
a
look
that
was
as
