flows.
And
should
the
question
arise,
you
joined
the
council
yesterday.”

“Yester—”
A
fit
of
coughing
bent
him
over.
“Yesterday.
To
be
sure.”
Lord
Gyles
coughed
into
a
square
of
red
silk,
as
if
to
hide
the
blood
in
his
