for
a
fortnight.
“Let
all
of
King’s
Landing
see
the
flames.
It
will
be
a
lesson
to
our
enemies.”

“Now
you
sound
like
Aerys.”

Her
nostrils
flared.
“Guard
your
tongue,
ser.”

“I
love
you
too,
sweet
sister.”

How
could
I
ever
have
loved
that
wretched
creature?
she
wondered
after
he
had
gone.
He
was
your
twin,
your
shadow,
your
other
half,
another
