whispered.
Once,
perhaps,
she
thought.
No
longer.
He
has
become
a
stranger
to
me.

Compared
to
the
magnificence
of
Joffrey’s
nuptials,
the
wedding
of
King
Tommen
was
a
modest
affair,
and
small.
No
one
wanted
another
lavish
ceremony,
least
of
all
the
queen,
and
no
