Cersei
herself
was
still
in
black,
as
a
sign
of
mourning
for
her
murdered
firstborn.
His
widow
might
be
pleased
to
laugh
and
drink
and
dance
and
put
all
memory
of
Joff
aside,
but
his
mother
would
not
forget
him
so
