This
is
wrong,
she
thought.
It
is
too
soon.
A
year,
two
years,
that
would
have
been
time
enough.
Highgarden
should
have
been
content
with
a
betrothal.
Cersei
stared
back
to
where
Mace
Tyrell
stood
between
his
wife
and
mother.
You
forced
me
into
this
travesty
of
a
wedding,
my
lord,
and
I
shall
not
soon
forget
it.

When
it
was
time
for
the
changing
of
