Rock...”

Your
service
was
required
here.
Cersei
had
named
her
cousin
Damion
Lannister
her
castellan
for
the
Rock,
and
another
cousin,
Ser
Daven
Lannister,
the
Warden
of
the
West.
Insolence
has
its
price,
Uncle.
“Bring
