“My
little
love
needs
to
take
smaller
sips.
See,
you
scared
your
lady
mother
half
to
death.”

“I’m
sorry,
Mother,”
Tommen
said,
abashed.

It
was
more
than
Cersei
could
stand.
I
cannot
let
them
see
me
cry,
she
thought,
when
she
felt
the
tears
welling
in
her
