you
are
holding
a—”

“—needle,”
Arya
finished
for
him,
fiercely.

“Just
so.
Now
we
will
begin
the
dance.
Remember,
child,
this
is
not
the
iron
dance
of
Westeros
we
are
learning,
the
knight’s
