swift
and
sudden.
All
men
are
made
of
water,
do
you
know
this?
When
you
pierce
them,
the
water
leaks
out
and
they
die.”
He
took
a
step
backward,
raised
his
own
wooden
blade.
“Now
you
will
try
to
strike
me.”

Arya
tried
to
strike
him.
She
tried
for
four
hours,
until
every
muscle
in
her
body
was
sore
and
aching,
while
Syrio
Forel
clicked
his
teeth
together
and
told
her
what
to
do.

The
next
day
their
real
work
began.
