me!”

“My
vows...”

“...did
not
stop
you
slaying
Aerys.
Words
are
wind.
You
could
have
had
me,
but
you
chose
a
cloak
instead.
Get
out.”

“Sister...”

“Get
out,
I
said.
I
am
sick
of
looking
at
that
ugly
stump
of
yours.
Get
out!”
To
speed
him
on
