way,
she
heaved
her
wine
cup
at
his
head.
She
missed,
but
Jaime
took
the
hint.

Evenfall
found
him
sitting
alone
in
the
common
room
of
White
Sword
Tower,
with
a
cup
of
Dornish
red
and
