and
died
screaming.
The
lesson
is,
men
who
wear
white
breeches
need
to
keep
them
tightly
laced.”

“Gyles
Greycloak?
Orivel
the
Open-Handed?”

“Gyles
was
a
traitor,
Orivel
a
coward.
Men
who
shamed
the
white
cloak.
What
is
