No,
Cersei
decided.
=======
say.
“We’ll
find
a
horse
for
you,
I
promise,”
Robb
whispered
at
last.

“Are
they
ever
coming
back?”
Bran
asked
him.

“Yes,”
Robb
said
with
such
hope
in
his
voice
that
Bran
knew
