asked
Merryweather.

“He
dare
not.
The
onion
knight’s
head
is
the
coin
he’ll
need
to
buy
his
son’s
life.”
Cersei
smiled.
“The
fat
old
fool
may
have
been
loyal
to
the
Starks
in
