She
shared
my
hearth
and
hall,
played
with
my
own
children.
I
fed
her,
dressed
her,
tried
to
make
her
a
little
less
ignorant
about
the
world,
and
how
did
she
repay
me
for
my
kindness?
She
helped
murder
my
son.
When
we
find
the
Imp,
we
will
find
the
Lady
Sansa
too.
She
is
not
dead...
but
before
I
am
done
with
her,
I
promise
