she
will
be
singing
to
the
Stranger,
begging
for
his
kiss.”

An
awkward
silence
followed.
Have
they
all
swallowed
their
tongues?
Cersei
thought,
with
irritation.
It
was
enough
to
make
her
wonder
why
she
bothered
with
a
council.

“In
any
case,”
the
queen
went
on,
“Lord
Eddard’s
younger
daughter
is
with
Lord
Bolton,
and
will
be
wed
to
his
son
Ramsay
as
