The
bruise
those
words
had
won
her
had
been
hard
to
hide
from
Jaime,
but
they
heard
no
more
about
the
bastard
girl.
Catelyn
Tully
was
a
mouse,
or
she
would
have
smothered
this
Jon
Snow
in
