red?”

“Love.”
It
was
Cersei’s
turn
to
laugh.
“She
fancies
our
Ser
Osney.”
He
was
the
youngest
Kettleblack,
the
clean-shaved
one.
Though
he
had
the
same
black
hair,
hooked
nose,
and
easy
