as
his
brother
Osmund,
one
cheek
bore
three
long
scratches,
courtesy
of
one
of
Tyrion’s
whores.
“She
likes
his
scars,
I
think.”

Lady
Merryweather’s
dark
eyes
shone
with
mischief.
“Just
so.
Scars
make
a
man
look
dangerous,
and
danger
is
exciting.”

“You
shock
me,
my
