Wall.”

“The
Wall?”
he
said
with
dismay.

It
was
all
she
could
do
not
to
laugh.
No,
best
not.
Men
hate
being
laughed
at.
“A
black
cloak
would
go
well
with
your
eyes,
and
that
black
hair
of
yours.”

“No
one
returns
from
the
Wall.”

“You
will.
All
