kill
a
boy.”

“What
boy?”

“A
bastard
boy
in
league
with
Stannis.
He’s
young
and
green,
and
you’ll
have
a
hundred
men.”

Kettleblack
was
afraid,
she
could
smell
it
on
him,
but
he
was
too
proud
to
own
up
to
that
fear.
Men
are
all
alike.
“I’ve
killed
more
boys
than
I
can
