Tyrion
wondered
whether
the
boy
would
think
the
adventure
quite
so
splendid
once
the
Lannister
riders
caught
up
with
them.

The
rain
had
finally
stopped
and
dawn
light
was
seeping
through
the
wet
cloth
over
his
eyes
when
Catelyn
Stark
gave
the
command
to
