You
write
of
defending
Lord
Robert
even
as
you
deny
him
food.
That
must
end.
I
am
no
warrior,
but
I
will
fight
you
if
you
do
not
lift
this
siege.
There
are
other
lords
besides
you
in
the
Vale,
and
King’s
Landing
will
send
men
as
well.
If
it
is
war
you
want,
say
so
now
and
the
Vale
will
bleed.”

Alayne
could
see
the
doubt
blooming
in
the
eyes
of
the
Lords
Declarant.
“A
year
is
not
so
long
