You
must
swear
to
that
as
well.”

“Gladly,”
said
Petyr.
“It
is
friends
I
want,
not
foes.
I
shall
pardon
all
of
you,
in
writing
if
you
wish.
Even
Lyn
Corbray.
His
brother
is
a
good
man,
there
is
no
need
to
bring
down
