“Did
you
see?”
he
was
asking
everyone.
“I
did
it
just
the
way
Ser
Loras
said.
Did
you
see,
Ser
Osney?”

“I
did,”
said
Osney
Kettleblack.
“A
pretty
sight.”

“You
have
a
better
seat
than
me,
sire,”
put
in
Ser
Dermot.

“I
broke
the
lance
too.
Ser
Loras,
did
you
hear
it?”

“As
loud
as
a
crack
of
