I
think.”
Her
three
cousins
all
agreed,
and
the
wretched
little
Bulwer
girl
began
to
hop
about,
chanting,
“Tommen
will
be
the
champion,
the
champion,
the
champion.”

“When
he
is
a
man
grown,”
said
Cersei.

Their
smiles
withered
like
