Pray
tell
us,
Your
Grace,
what
tourneys
did
he
win?
What
great
knights
did
he
unseat?
I
know
the
king
should
like
to
hear
about
his
father’s
victories.”

A
flush
crept
up
Cersei’s
neck.
The
girl
had
caught
her
out.
Robert
Baratheon
had
been
an
indifferent
jouster,
in
truth.
During
tourneys
he
had
much
