sweetly.
“Lord
Renly,
was
it
not?”

“I
had
that
honor.”

“Yes,
I
thought
as
much.”
Cersei
had
seen
how
tight
the
bonds
grew
between
squires
and
the
knights
they
served.
She
did
not
want
Tommen
growing
close
to
Loras
Tyrell.
The
Knight
of
Flowers
was
no
sort
of
man
for
any
boy
to
