that
only
Cersei
ever
saw.
“Not
until
His
Grace
agrees
to
the
betrothal.
It
must
remain
our
secret
for
now.”
And
so
it
had,
though
once
she
had
drawn
a
picture
of
herself
flying
behind
Rhaegar
on
a
