her
arms
wrapped
tight
about
his
chest.
When
Jaime
had
discovered
it
she
told
him
it
was
Queen
Alysanne
and
King
Jaehaerys.

She
was
ten
when
she
finally
saw
her
prince
in
the
flesh,
at
the
tourney
her
lord
father
had
thrown
to
welcome
King
Aerys
to
the
west.
Viewing
stands
had
been
raised
beneath
the
walls
of
Lannisport,
and
the
