as
they
cheered
Prince
Rhaegar.

Seventeen
and
new
to
knighthood,
Rhaegar
Targaryen
had
worn
black
plate
over
golden
ringmail
when
he
cantered
onto
the
lists.
Long
streamers
of
red
and
gold
and
orange
