along
with
a
dozen
of
her
father’s
finest
jousters,
the
flower
of
the
west.
By
night
the
prince
played
his
silver
harp
and
made
her
weep.
When
she
had
been
presented
to
him,
Cersei
had
almost
drowned
in
the
depths
of
his
sad
