“but
this
is
the
house
of
the
gods.”

Color
rose
to
her
cheeks.
One
word
to
Meryn
Trant,
and
the
stoop-backed
greybeard
would
be
meeting
his
gods
sooner
than
he
might
have
liked.
Not
here,
though.
Not
now.
“Wait
for
