“Your
Grace.”

“Septon
Raynard?”
The
queen
could
scarce
believe
what
she
was
seeing.
“What
are
you
doing
on
your
knees?”

“He
is
cleaning
the
floor.”
The
speaker
was
shorter
than
the
queen
by
