She
had
never
truly
believed
that
he
was
harboring
the
Imp.
Her
twisted
little
brother
was
too
clever
to
allow
Lollys
to
name
her
wretched
ill-begotten
bastard
after
him,
knowing
it
was
sure
to
draw
the
queen’s
wroth
down
