“Yes,”
said
Lady
Merryweather.

“And
this?”
Cersei
pinched
the
nipple
now,
pulling
on
it
hard,
twisting
it
between
her
fingers.

The
Myrish
woman
gave
a
gasp
of
pain.
“You’re
hurting
me.”

“It’s
just
the
wine.
I
had
a
flagon
with
my
