her
calm.”
She
twisted
Taena’s
other
nipple
too,
pulling
until
the
other
woman
gasped.
“I
am
the
queen.
I
mean
to
claim
my
rights.”

“Do
what
you
will.”
Taena’s
hair
was
as
black
as
Robert’s,
even
down
