She
could
not
feel
it,
whatever
Robert
felt
on
the
nights
he
took
her.
There
was
no
pleasure
in
it,
not
for
her.
For
Taena,
yes.
Her
nipples
were
two
black
diamonds,
her
sex
slick
and
