were
covered
with
manure,
and
he
had
a
pitchfork
in
one
hand.
“Who
are
you?”
she
asked.

“She
don’t
know
me,”
he
said,
“but
I
knows
her,
oh,
yes.
The
wolf
girl.”

“Help
me
saddle
a
horse,”
Arya
pleaded,
reaching
back
into
the
chest,
groping
for
Needle.
“My
father’s
the
Hand
of
the
King,
he’ll
reward
