Jaime
lifted
his
own
cup
left-handed
and
took
a
swallow.
The
warmth
spread
through
his
chest.
“You
were
speaking
of
the
Freys
you
wanted
dead.
Ryman,
Edwyn,
Emmon...”

“And
Walder
Rivers,”
Daven
said,
“that
whoreson.
Hates
that
he’s
a
bastard,
and
hates
everyone
who’s
not.
Ser
Perwyn
seems
a
decent
fellow,
though,
might
as
well
spare
