The
women
too.
I’m
to
marry
one,
I
hear.
Your
father
might
have
seen
fit
to
consult
with
me
about
this
marriage,
by
the
bye.
My
own
father
was
treating
with
Paxter
Redwyne
before
Oxcross,
did
