“If
my
choice
is
Freys
or
freckles,
well...
half
of
Lord
Walder’s
brood
look
like
stoats.”

“Only
half?
Be
thankful.
I
saw
Lancel’s
bride
at
Darry.”

“Gatehouse
Ami,
gods
be
good.
I
couldn’t
believe
that
Lancel
picked
that
one.
What’s
wrong
with
that
boy?”

“He’s
grown
pious,”
said
Jaime,
“but
it
wasn’t
