he
brings
forth
Edmure
Tully,
drapes
a
noose
around
his
neck,
and
threatens
to
hang
him
unless
the
castle
yields.
The
Blackfish
pays
his
mummer’s
show
no
mind,
so
come
evenfall
Lord
Edmure
is
taken
down
again.
His
wife’s
with
child,
did
you
know?”

He
hadn’t.
“Edmure
bedded
her,
after
the
Red
Wedding?”

“He
was
bedding
her
during
the
Red
Wedding.
Roslin’s
a
pretty
little
thing,
hardly
stoatish
at
all.
And
fond
of
Edmure,
queerly.
Perwyn
tells
me
she’s
