“Tell
me
of
your
dispositions,
coz.”

“We
have
the
castle
well
encircled.
Ser
Ryman
and
the
Freys
are
north
of
the
Tumblestone.
South
of
Red
Fork
sits
Lord
Emmon,
with
Ser
Forley
Prester
and
with
what
