We’ve
thrown
a
boom
across
the
Red
Fork,
downstream
of
the
castle.
Manfryd
Yew
and
Raynard
Ruttiger
have
charge
of
its
defense,
so
no
one
can
escape
by
boat.
I
gave
them
nets
as
well,
to
fish.
It
helps
keep
us
fed.”

“Can
we
starve
the
castle
out?”

Ser
Daven
shook
his
head.
“The
Blackfish
expelled
all
the
useless
mouths
from
Riverrun
and
picked
this
country
clean.
He
has
enough
stores
to
keep
man
and
horse
alive
for
two
