hissssssssssssssss.
The
man
in
the
Hound’s
helm
began
to
laugh.
“You’re
even
uglier
than
I
remembered.
I’d
sooner
rape
your
horse.”

“Horses,
that’s
what
we
want,”
one
of
the
wounded
men
said.
“Fresh
horses,
and
some
food.
There
are
outlaws
after
us.
Give
us
your
horses
and
we’ll
be
gone.
We
won’t
do
you
harm.”

“Fuck
that.”
The
outlaw
in
the
Hound’s
helm
yanked
a
battle
