so
she
can
watch
me
fuck
the
crossbow
girl.”

“With
what?”
taunted
Brienne.
“Shagwell
said
they
cut
your
manhood
off
when
they
took
your
nose.”

She
meant
it
to
provoke
him,
and
it
did.
Bellowing
