Dance
she
did,
relieved
that
they
were
watching.
Better
that
than
have
them
interfere.
She
could
not
fight
seven,
not
alone,
even
if
one
or
two
were
wounded.
Old
Ser
Goodwin
was
long
in
his
grave,
yet
she
could
hear
him
whispering
in
her
