it
was
a
corpse
that
she
embraced,
there
in
the
black
rain.
She
stepped
back
and
let
him
fall...

...and
Biter
crashed
into
her,
shrieking.

He
fell
on
her
like
an
avalanche
of
wet
wool
and
milk-white
flesh,
lifting
her
off
her
feet
and
slamming
her
down
into
