but
shall...”

“...unless
I
hand
you
Riverrun.
Is
this
where
you
threaten
to
hang
Edmure?”
Beneath
his
bushy
brows,
Tully’s
eyes
were
stone.
“My
nephew
is
marked
for
death
no
matter
what
I
do.
So
hang
him
and
be
