“If
Lord
Tywin
wants
my
help,
he
can
bloody
well
ask
for
it.”

That
was
all
Catelyn
needed
to
hear.
“I
am
asking
for
your
help,
my
lord,”
she
said
humbly.
“And
my
father
and
my
brother
and
my
lord
husband
and
my
sons
are
asking
with
my
