it.
Sweet
words
he
gave
me,
excuses,
but
what
I
wanted
was
to
get
rid
of
a
daughter.

“And
your
sister,
that
one,
she’s
full
as
bad.
It
was,
oh,
a
year
ago,
no
more,
Jon
Arryn
was
still
the
King’s
Hand,
and
I
went
