is,
the
slash
opened
her
cheek
down
to
the
bone
and
sliced
off
her
right
ear.
Maester
Caleotte
was
able
to
save
her
life,
but
no
poultice
nor
potion
will
ever
restore
her
face.
She
was
my
ward,
Arianne.
Betrothed
to
your
own
brother
and
under
my
protection.
You
have
dishonored
all
of
us.”

“I
never
meant
her
harm,”
Arianne
insisted.
“If
Hotah
had
not
