against
her
brother.
Instead
of
an
ear,
she
would
have
lost
her
life.”

“Only
if
we
lost.”

“If?
The
word
is
when.
Dorne
is
the
least
populous
of
the
Seven
Kingdoms.
It
pleased
the
Young
Dragon
to
make
all
our
armies
larger
when
he
wrote
that
book
of
his,
so
as
to
make
his
conquest
that
much
more
glorious,
and
it
has
pleased
us
to
water
the
seed
he
planted
and
let
our
foes
think
us
more
powerful
than
we
are,
but
a
princess
ought
to
know
the
truth.
Valor
is
a
poor
