for
numbers.
Dorne
cannot
hope
to
win
a
war
against
the
Iron
Throne,
not
alone.
And
yet
that
may
well
be
what
you
have
given
us.
Are
you
proud?”
The
prince
did
not
allow
her
time
to
answer.
“What
am
I
to
do
with
you,
Arianne?”

Forgive
me,
part
of
her
wanted
to
say,
but
his
words
had
cut
