“Why,
do
what
you
always
do.
Do
nothing.”

“You
make
it
difficult
for
a
man
to
swallow
his
anger.”

“Best
stop
swallowing,
you’re
like
to
choke
on
it.”
The
prince
did
not
answer.
“Tell
me
how
you
knew
my
plans.”

“I
am
the
Prince
of
Dorne.
Men
seek
my
favor.”

Someone
told.
“You
knew,
and
