princess.”
Prince
Doran
sighed.
“You
disappoint
me,
Arianne.”

“Said
the
crow
to
the
raven.
You
have
been
disappointing
me
for
years,
Father.”
She
had
not
meant
to
be
so
blunt
with
him,
but
the
words
came
spilling
out.
There,
now
I
have
said
it.

“I
know.
I
am
too
meek
and
weak
and
cautious,
too
lenient
to
our
enemies.
Just
now,
though,
you
are
in
need
