he
had
whispered,
“We
should
not
be
doing
this,”
she
would
be
richer
than
the
Lannisters.
Did
he
charge
at
Areo
Hotah
in
hopes
of
saving
me?
Arianne
wondered.
Or
did
he
do
it
to
escape
me,
to
wash
out
