in
the
queen’s
shame.
Lady
Megga
and
Lady
Elinor
were
examined
as
well.
Both
were
found
to
have
been
broken.”

The
wasps
were
growing
so
loud
that
the
queen
could
hardly
hear
herself
think.
I
do
hope
the
little
queen
and
her
cousins
enjoyed
those
rides
of
theirs.

Lord
Merryweather
thumped
his
fist
on
the
table.
“Lady
Margaery
had
sworn
solemn
oaths
attesting
to
her
maidenhood,
to
Her
Grace
the
queen
and
her
late
father.
Many
here
bore
