wash
over
her
for
a
few
heartbeats,
savoring
the
sounds
of
the
little
queen’s
disgrace.
When
it
had
gone
on
long
enough,
she
rose
stone-faced
and
commanded
that
the
gold
cloaks
clear
the
hall.
Margaery
Tyrell
is
done,
she
thought,
exulting.
Her
white
knights
fell
in
