her
as
she
made
her
exit
through
the
king’s
door
behind
the
Iron
Throne;
Boros
Blount,
Meryn
Trant,
and
Osmund
Kettleblack,
the
last
of
the
Kingsguard
still
remaining
in
the
city.

Moon
Boy
was
standing
beside
the
door,
holding
his
rattle
in
