of
House
Lannister,



—{LADY},
her
direwolf,
killed
at
Castle
Darry,





—ARYA,
a
girl
of
eleven,
missing
and
thought
dead,



—NYMERIA,
her
direwolf,
prowling
the
riverlands,





—BRANDON,
called
BRAN,
a
crippled
boy
of
nine,
heir
to
