HOUSE
TARGARYEN
>>>>>>> asd

The
Targaryens
are
the
blood
of
the
dragon,
descended
from
the
high
lords
of
the
ancient
Freehold
of
Valyria,
their
heritage
<<<<<<< 1441d55ef0d8b5e242e34427404d9d5041159095
marked
by
lilac,
indigo,
and
=======
proclaimed
in
a
striking
(some
say
inhuman)
beauty,
with
lilac
or
indigo
or
>>>>>>> asd
violet
eyes
and
hair
of
<<<<<<< 1441d55ef0d8b5e242e34427404d9d5041159095
silver-gold.
To
preserve
their
blood
=======
silver-gold
or
platinum
white.



Aegon
the
Dragon’s
ancestors
escaped
the
Doom
of
Valyria
and
the
chaos
and
slaughter
that
followed
to
settle
on
Dragonstone,
a
rocky
island
in
the
narrow
sea.
It
was
from
there
that
Aegon
and
his
sisters
sailed
to
conquer
the
Seven
Kingdoms.
To
preserve
the
blood
royal
>>>>>>> asd
and
keep
it
pure,
House
Targaryen
has
<<<<<<< 1441d55ef0d8b5e242e34427404d9d5041159095
oft
wed
brother
to
sister,
cousin
to
cousin,
uncle
to
niece.
The
founder
of
the
dynasty,
Aegon
the
Conquerer,
=======
often
followed
the
Valyrian
custom
of
wedding
brother
to
sister.
Aegon
himself
>>>>>>> asd
took
both
his
sisters
to
<<<<<<< 1441d55ef0d8b5e242e34427404d9d5041159095
wife
=======
wife,
>>>>>>> asd
and
fathered
sons
on
each.
The
Targaryen
banner
is
a
three-headed
dragon,
red
on
black,
the
three
heads
representing
Aegon
and
his
sisters.
The
Targaryen
words
are
Fire
and
Blood.



